The new book, &quot;Everyday Anarchy&quot; by Stefan Molyneux. Discussed is the philosophical concept of anarchy, how it is the basis of government, and our social and political contradictions about anarchy.

Philosophical anarchy is not about blood and guts chaos, but about living without government in a peaceful manner. You may be surprised to learn that you engage in anarchy every single day.

